        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Fair Campaign Communications Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Election Commission to study and report on the practices and procedures used by email providers to classify emails from political campaigns (e.g., classifying such emails as spam).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
